        "subject": "LU-4000 lloop: Fix build failure on ppc64",
        "message": "LU-4000 lloop: Fix build failure on ppc64\n\nCommit e7246c5e (LU-4000 lloop: Fix build failure) introduced\na regression where other parts of the code couldn't handle\nsplit bios that are generated via directio.\n\nThis patch restores the original behavior but allows splitting\nof bios on systems with 64k pages instead of failing to build.\n\nChange-Id: I99cc603a89f8902322139864ab179b565f281e57\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\n"
